{"TopicId":135530,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.2; obsolete] NavBallsToYou - make the navball appear automagically in map view","CreatedByName":"Cerebrate","CreatedById":110690,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-31T16:12:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cerebrate","CreatedById":110690,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-31T16:12:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003ENOTE: technically, this mod is obsolete, since unsetting the \u0022Autohide navball\u0022 setting in stock now duplicates its functionality. I\u0027m leaving the download available, however, to ease transition, but it will not be updated beyond 1.2.\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom my epic impatience to yours, seeing as not having this functionality available turns out to be... a considerable irritation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod shows the navball automatically whenever you enter map view. No more, no less.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGet it here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/cerebrate/NavBallsToYou/releases/tag/0.2\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/cerebrate/NavBallsToYou/releases/tag/0.2\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0or here\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/458/NavBallsToYou\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://spacedock.info/mod/458/NavBallsToYou\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSource here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/cerebrate/NavBallsToYou\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/cerebrate/NavBallsToYou\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense: public domain.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-c\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-15T17:53:04Z\u0022 title=\u002210/15/2016 05:53  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Cerebrate\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eobsolescence\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"meyerweb","CreatedById":135212,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-31T16:45:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, I am \u003Cem\u003Eso\u003C/em\u003E installing this when I upgrade to 1.1.\u00A0 Thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr Shifty","CreatedById":68146,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T03:12:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery nice. I still don\u0027t understand why this isn\u0027t standard behavior. Who doesn\u0027t immediately pull up the NavBall immediately upon entering the map view every time?\u00A0Now if we could just stage from map view...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kendoka15","CreatedById":85678,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T03:37:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n^ This.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks very much \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CloudlessEchoes","CreatedById":142599,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-25T03:32:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems to work in release too, great mod I was so sick of expanding it every single time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"problemecium","CreatedById":101649,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-05T03:45:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat all the previous posters said. This is literally a missing feature from the game. The fact that it has yet to be made stock is almost worthy of being called a bug xD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cerebrate","CreatedById":110690,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T03:10:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNavBallsToYou is now updated for KSP 1.2. Enjoy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-c\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeorge","CreatedById":1544