o, Met said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a helpful quality of life mod. Thanks for keeping it updated!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, but now we have an option in KSP settings that makes this useful mod obsolete.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jiraiyah","CreatedById":97667,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T12:25:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222805432\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135530\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221476534024\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279159\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lajoswinkler\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, lajoswinkler said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, but now we have an option in KSP settings that makes this useful mod obsolete.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI saw people talking about that setting, where can i find it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Torih","CreatedById":144304,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-15T12:40:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222805436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135530\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221476534342\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002297667\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jiraiyah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Jiraiyah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u