e, \u0022Hey, it\u0027s about time we do this ourselves\u0022. \u00A0Thanks for all the good times \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110690-cerebrate/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022110690\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/110690-cerebrate/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Cerebrate\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and for keeping the bar doors open a few hours past closing time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sjwt","CreatedById":9268,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-18T02:04:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIndeed, there is no reason to close this thread down, a slight trim maybe, lets keep this thread open and nice guys.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}